### Secrets ###
# Ignore local environment files.
# Instead, commit example files (e.g., env.sh.example, .env.example).
/workspaces/accordinnovations/backend/env.sh
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

### Dependencies ###
# Ignore dependency directories installed by package managers.
/node_modules
/vendor
/bower_components

### Build & Compilation ###
# Ignore build output and compiled files.
/build
/dist
/out
/target
.next/
.nuxt/
.svelte-kit/

### Logs ###
# Ignore log files from various tools.
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
yarn-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

### IDE & Editor Directories ###
# Ignore settings files from common code editors.
.idea/
.vscode/
*.sublime-workspace
*.sublime-project

### OS-generated Files ###
# Ignore files generated by macOS, Windows, and Linux systems.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

### Test & Coverage Reports ###
/coverage
.nyc_output